premise_source_doc_sentence: The Last Kingdom is a British historical fiction television series based on Bernard Cornwell 's The Saxon Stories series of novels .
The first two novels in the series were adapted for television in 2015 as The Last Kingdom .
Chimor was the last kingdom that had any chance of stopping the Inca Empire .
Finally , the last kingdom was centered on Meroë  (  300 BC -- AD 300  )  .

The Saxon Stories  (  also known as `` Saxon Tales '' / `` Saxon Chronicles '' in the USA and `` The Warrior Chronicles '' and since the BBC TV adaptation as `` The Last Kingdom Series '' in the UK  )  is a continuing historical novel series written by Bernard Cornwell about 9th and 10th century Britain .
